snippet.title: thehardwareguy
snippet.description:
My name is Gareth. I'm an Engineer/Maker. I also love to teach. For all things Electronics, DIY, CAD and 3D Printing... be sure to subscribe!

I'm open to talking about business enquires. Feel free to send me an email.
